    "Risk-taking is a step that moderates the leadership and organizational innovations in the company.",
    "• Decision-making is the final step where leaders in an organization encourage employees to create more ideas towards innovations.",
    "Such creativity and innovations bring more success and generate new opportunities and growth in the business, regardless of whether the business is developing a product or providing new services to customers (Mokhber et al. 2018).",
